message.entry: The input must be a double precision, column vector with more than 1 element.
The AdjacentMeasurementBandwidth property must be a scalar or a row vector with a length equal to the AdjacentChannelOffset property vector length.
The specified measurement bands are outside the Nyquist interval of [-SampleRate/2 SampleRate/2] when NormalizedFrequency is false, or [-1 1] when NormalizedFrequency is true.
